  "fullArabic": "وَلِيَعۡلَمَ ٱلَّذِينَ نَافَقُواْۚ وَقِيلَ لَهُمۡ تَعَالَوۡاْ قَٰتِلُواْ فِي سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ أَوِ ٱدۡفَعُواْۖ قَالُواْ لَوۡ نَعۡلَمُ قِتَالٗا لَّٱتَّبَعۡنَٰكُمۡۗ هُمۡ لِلۡكُفۡرِ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَقۡرَبُ مِنۡهُمۡ لِلۡإِيمَٰنِۚ يَقُولُونَ بِأَفۡوَٰهِهِم مَّا لَيۡسَ فِي قُلُوبِهِمۡۚ وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يَكۡتُمُونَ",
  "fullTranslation": "And that He might make evident those who are hypocrites. For it was said to them, \"Come, fight in the way of Allah or [at least] defend.\" They said, \"If we had known [there would be] fighting, we would have followed you.\" They were nearer to disbelief that day than to faith, saying with their mouths what was not in their hearts. And Allah is most Knowing of what they conceal -",
  "fullTransliteration": "waliya'lama alladhina nafaqu waqila lahum ta'alaw qatilu fi sabili al-lahi awi id'fa'u qalu law na'lamu qitalan la-ittaba'nakum hum lil'kuf'ri yawma-idhin aqrabu min'hum lil'imani yaquluna bi-afwahihim ma laysa fi qulubihim wal-lahu a'lamu bima yaktumuna"
}
